* Slow NMOS, Fast PMOS: Asymmetric skew  
* Slow NMOS (high Vth, low mobility)
* Fast PMOS (low |Vth|, high mobility)

* Process skew parameters (if supported by models)
* .param NMOS_VTH_SHIFT=0.05
* .param PMOS_VTH_SHIFT=0.05
* .param NMOS_MOBILITY_MULT=0.9
* .param PMOS_MOBILITY_MULT=1.1
